name: Holi
description:
This beautiful pieces which portrays one of India's most influential and spiritual festivals. 

'Holi' is now available for purchase on archival standard art paper. 

I print all my pieces are on genuine 100% rag, mould-made watercolour paper.  This french paper gives each piece a wonderful authentic texture and depth. Because i use professional archival materials, these prints are durable, acid free and fade resisent - a perfect addition to your wall.

Each art print is printed, signed and packaged with lots of love and care :)

Don't be shy to contact me with any questions or enquiries about other sizes etc

Stephanie
